snippet: The Olympic star Sun Yang picked up his second gold medal of the Asian swimming championships in Dubai as the Chinese dominated for a second straight day.
abstract: China's Sun Yang wins 400-meter freestyle event at Asian swimming championships in Dubai; other swimming news noted.
